nhc_headline: ...KELI OPENS INTO A TROUGH... ...THIS IS THE LAST ADVISORY...
summary: ...KELI OPENS INTO A TROUGH... ...THIS IS THE LAST ADVISORY... As of 11:00 AM HST Wed Jul 30 the center of Keli was located near 13.9, -156.6 with movement W at 17 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1006 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
